data.chText: 英国保守党党员（或支持者）
data.enText: a member or supporter of the British Conservative party

data.chText: 英国保守党在选举中失败。
data.enText: The Tories (= the Tory party) lost the election.

means: 英国保守党党员(或支持者)

value.def: In Britain, a Tory politician or voter is a member of or votes for the Conservative Party.

example.ex: ...the former Tory Party chairman, Chris Patten.
…the constituency with the largest Tory majority in the country.
example.tran: 该国托利党多数票的票数居首的选区

example.ex: ...the first female leader of the Tories.

value.tran: (英国)托利党党员的，保守党党员的
